      "span_text": "While  argued that the test has a fairly efficient bubble-detection method in one or two bubble alternatives, PSY (2013) showed that although the PWY procedure consistently estimates the start date of the first bubble in any sample in case of two bubble alternatives, it may fail to identify the second bubble."
